description: TEHRAN – Tehran’s ambassador to Yerevan has dismissed reports of a military agreement between Iran and Armenia, saying such rumors are spread by those who have a biased view toward Iran.
title: Military agreement between Iran and Armenia is dismissed

description: TEHRAN - In a note, Kayhan addressed the difficulty of an Iran-U.S. agreement and wrote: Returning to the JCPOA will be on the table again after the U.S. presidential election in November.
title: America won’t lift sanctions and Iran won’t trust America

description: TEHRAN - The summer of 1988 witnessed a dramatic clash between Iran and the Mujahedin-e Khalq (aka MEK, MKO, PMOI) terrorist group. In the wake of an eight-year war with Iraq, Iran faced a renewed threat on its western borders.
title: The Eternal Illusion

description: EU foreign policy chief Josep Borrell has slammed Israel’s advance of laws labelling UNRWA as a ‘terrorist’ organization, amid a push to discredit the UN agency for Palestinian refugees.
title: EU’s Borrell says labelling UNRWA as ‘terrorist’ is ‘nonsense’

description: A new wave of air strikes by Israeli fighter jets have targeted the central areas of Gaza, Al Jazeera correspondent Tareq Abu Azzoum reported from Deir el-Balah on Thursday.
title: ‘Snipers shooting anyone who moves’ in Khan Younis: Al Jazeera

description: Israel’s widespread destruction of housing in Gaza may amount to war crimes, according to a UN expert.
title: UN expert: Large-scale destruction of housing in Gaza is a war crime

description: In recent weeks, the Israeli regime has accelerated its attacks on the core institutions and valued representatives of the United Nations in an effort to conceal the truth about its countless international and humanitarian law violations in Gaza and the rest of the illegally occupied Palestinian territories.
title: The ICJ compelled the international community to take action against Israel

description: Qatar has welcomed the signing of the “Beijing Declaration” by Palestinian factions earlier this week to achieve reconciliation and strengthen unity against Israeli “violations” in all the occupied territory.
title: Qatar welcomes China-hosted reconciliation of Palestinian factions

description: TEHRAN – The Iranian Foreign Ministry has strongly criticized the United States for warmly welcoming “criminal” Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu despite butchering and maiming tens of thousands of Palestinians in the Gaza Strip since October 2023.
title: Iran lambasts US for embracing 'criminal' Netanyahu

description: TEHRAN – Iran defeated Qatar 3-0 (25-11, 25-10, 25-11) in the 2024 Asian Men's U20 Volleyball Championship on Thursday.
title: Iran defeat Qatar at 2024 Asian U20 Volleyball Championship
